---
layout: "_layouts/blogs-layout.njk"
title: "Blog"
---

<p>
    These arent really gonna be real blog posts because I'm lazy but more like a paragraph of schizo posting.
    <a href="/feed.xml">Click this to get the rss feed.</a>.
</p>

<p>Posts:</p>
<ul class="blog-list">
  {% for blog in collections.blog | reverse %}
    {% set wordCount = blog.templateContent | wordCount %}
    {% set readTime = blog.templateContent | readTime %}
    <li style="margin: 10px;">
      <a href="{{ blog.url }}">{{ blog.data.title }}</a> 
      <span style="color: #c6a0f6">
        {{ blog.date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'short', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' }).replace('.', '') }}
      </span> 
      - {{ wordCount }} words ({{ readTime }} min read)
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>